%% Expected Output / Sequence Diagram — Compose to Approved Execution
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Operator
    participant CC as Cursor Companion Composer
    participant API as Composer API Gateway
    participant REG as Registry Projection Service
    participant COMP as Composition Repository
    participant PIPE as Pipeline Compiler
    participant POL as Execution Policy Gateway
    participant RUN as Existing Run Control
    participant OBS as Session Projection / Evidence References

    Operator->>CC: Open composer dashboard
    CC->>API: Request building block library
    API->>REG: Refresh/read normalized registry
    REG-->>API: Building block library index
    API-->>CC: Building blocks

    Operator->>CC: Create composed agent configuration
    CC->>API: Validate and save composition
    API->>COMP: Persist composed-agent-configuration
    COMP-->>API: compositionRef
    API-->>CC: Saved composition reference

    Operator->>CC: Assemble orchestration pipeline
    CC->>API: Validate and save pipeline definition
    API->>COMP: Persist pipeline
    COMP-->>API: pipelineRef
    API-->>CC: Saved pipeline reference

    Operator->>CC: Compile pipeline to draft work orders
    CC->>API: compile(pipelineRef)
    API->>PIPE: Resolve blocks, lifecycle stages, and dependencies
    PIPE-->>API: Compilation result + draft work-order refs + required approvals
    API-->>CC: Compilation result

    Operator->>CC: Launch approved execution
    CC->>API: execution request(sourceRef, approvalRefs, action=start)
    API->>POL: Enforce approval/lifecycle/runtime policy
    POL->>RUN: Launch approved work-order run
    RUN-->>OBS: Run state + continuity ref + evidence target
    OBS-->>API: Session projection
    API-->>CC: queued / in_progress session state

    RUN-->>OBS: paused / failed / completed transitions
    OBS-->>CC: Live session updates
